        "created_at": "2026-01-04T00:35:39.730Z",
        "cooked": "<p>It might seem a bit unneccessary since a a chat with just one other person is way easier to follow than a group chat, but i think it would be a nice addition to have a place for notes both persons can edit. It would be great for a shopping list or to keep track of decisions you made for an upcomming vacation or just anything you want to remember together. And of course you can just use a group chat with just two members, but then you have to choose a good group name (since you cannot call it Person X) and then you have two chats for nearly the same purpose.</p>",
