        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/rassilon1963/{size}/31625_2.png",
        "created_at": "2026-01-04T12:51:20.572Z",
        "cooked": "<p>you can already set a note for contacts</p><aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"7\" data-topic=\"53623\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/awaitlink/48/48975_2.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <div class=\"quote-title__text-content\">\n      <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/personal-notes-on-contacts/53623/7\">Personal notes on contacts</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --style-square \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    Thanks <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/salt505\">@Salt505</a>.\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>\nthe ‚Äúeveryone can edit‚Äù sounds more like this:</p><aside class=\"quote quote-modified\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"57644\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/whatnoww/48/54328_2.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <div class=\"quote-title__text-content\">\n      <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/message-editable-by-everyone/57644\">Message editable by everyone</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --style-square \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    I feel it is extremely beneficial for Signal to find opportunities to get ahead of others. \nI‚Äôm suggesting there be a message type that is editable by everyone in a group chat or 1:1 chat. This would be useful for making lists. Right now some of my group chats get clogged with repeated messages where people are adding things to participation lists and such. \nI really feel this is something where Signal can get ahead of the rest. \nThis paired with a pinned message in a group would actually be ama‚Ä¶\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n",
